race.comment: PAW JENNEKE (1) was in the minors two back (25.54) at Shepparton but ran below best last time at Healesville, finishing 7th. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Can bounce back. OH SO BREE (5) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 410m behind Paw Brody (23.88) in a Grade 5. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from eight starts. Bold showing expected. LEKTRA ROGER (3) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten a head (23.69) behind Green Flash at this track. Expected to feature again. STEP ON AIR (2) is a last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.
